======================================================
Description: 	
A webcrawler to search twilio.com & all pages linked to on twilio.com
on the twilio domain for the word 'shenanigans', case insensitive.
Author: Jeffrey Sweeney
Date: 4/4/2012
======================================================

System Dependencies:
	perl runtime
	WWW::Mechanize library ($> cpanm WWW::Mechanize)

Usage:
	chmod +x shenanigans.pl
	shenanigans.pl
	